[13/10/2017 14:01:02] <font color="#ffffff">(Chirrido)</font>
[13/10/2017 14:01:37] <font color="#ffffff">(RÍE) No me has vencido,</font>
[13/10/2017 14:01:37] <font color="#ffffff">Tremal Naik.</font>
